# Dr. Santos' Enhanced Student Registry

## Project Description

Dr. Santos' Enhanced Student Registry is a C programming project that manages student records with file handling and data abstraction.

The original Student Registry only stored information temporarily in memory. This enhanced version uses file input/output operations so student records can be saved and loaded even after the program is closed.

The project demonstrates:
- Structures in C
- Header file abstraction
- Multi-file programming
- File handling using fopen(), fread(), fwrite(), and fclose()
- Data persistence


